First of all elbow macs are better, use those.

1. Make or buy any tomatoe sous you like
2. 200 gr of macs
3. Vegie mix
4. Paprica, cut in blocks by hand
5. Chanpignons cut slices
6. union, cut in pieces
7. Meatlovecow or vegie version
8. gehakt kruiden (for on the meat)
9. provinciaal kruiden (voor de vegies)
10. Salt and oil for the macs.

To do,
- Boil water, add oil and salt
- When boiling add the macs

- rull the meatlove and union and champignon in the big wok pan
- when meat is brown add the paprika and vegie mix
- cook till you feel its ready
- Add tomatoe souse
- cook till boil

- rince macs

putt all in pan and mix

serve with grates cheeeeeeeses
